Bind void to hanoi, given (the number n, the text source, the text target, the text aux):
    If n is 0:
        Return.
    Done.
    Cast hanoi on (n - 1, source, aux, target).
    State "Move disk " joined to (n converted to text) joined to " from " joined to source joined to " to " joined to target.
    Cast hanoi on (n - 1, aux, target, source).
Done.

Cast hanoi on (3, "A", "C", "B").
